      "comment": "REALITY SURPRISE (4) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 10 lengths at this track in a handy 24.15. Jumping from the pinch draw but goes well over this trip. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Expected to measure up again. MILLY LILY (7) is a progressive dog who scored her 2nd career win last time at this track, scoring by 1.3 lengths (24.49). Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. One of the key runners again. MANILA PLUTO (1) ran below best last time finishing fourth (30.72) over 525m at The Meadows in a Mix 6/7. Can measure up this time. LAKEVIEW TURBO (8) cannot be underestimated.",
